<xs:schema xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" version="1.0">
	<xs:element name="tsd_vorm" type="tsdVorm">
		<xs:annotation>
			<xs:documentation>
        Main table of Form TSD, contains general data concerning the person’s Form TSD
      </xs:documentation>
		</xs:annotation>
	</xs:element>
	<xs:complexType name="tsdVorm">
		<xs:all>
			<xs:element name="regKood">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Taxable person’s commercial register number or personal ID number</xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:string">
						<xs:maxLength value="20"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="c108_Aasta">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Year of the taxable period of the tax return</xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:long">
						<xs:totalDigits value="4"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="c109_Kuu">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Month of the taxable period of the tax return</xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:long">
						<xs:totalDigits value="2"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="laadimisViis" type="laadimisViisType">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Uploading method: L –addition of new tax return in preparation. If a tax return in preparation already exists in the same taxable period, it will be cancelled. P – Amendment of existing tax return in preparation and with the same taxable period to the extent of annexes contained in XML (i.e. if annexes in XML are 4, 5 and 6, they will be overwritten but annexes 1,2, 7, inf1 will remain intact). If such tax return in preparation does not exist, it will be created.</xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="vorm" type="vormType">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Tax return form, either TSD, ESD, XF11, XF12 or XF13
          </xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="c110_Tm" minOccurs="0">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Calculated: Income tax withheld (code 1250 - code 1550 + code 2250 - code 2550 + code 2800)      </xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:decimal">
						<xs:totalDigits value="22"/>
						<xs:fractionDigits value="2"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="c114_TmEj" minOccurs="0">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Calculated: Special income tax (code 3300 + code 4170 + code 5160 - code 5170 + code 5190 + code 6160 - code 6170 + code 7200 + code 8121)</xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:decimal">
						<xs:totalDigits value="22"/>
						<xs:fractionDigits value="2"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="c115_Sm" minOccurs="0">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Calculated: Social tax code 1210 + code 1211 - code 1510 + code 2210 + code 2211 - code 2510 + code 4180)</xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:decimal">
						<xs:totalDigits value="22"/>
						<xs:fractionDigits value="2"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="c116_Tk" minOccurs="0">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Calculated: Unemployment insurance premium (code 1230 + code 1240 + code 1231 + code 1241 - code 1530 - code 1540 + code 2220
            + code 2230 + code 2221 + code 2231 - code 2520 - code 2530)       </xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:decimal">
						<xs:totalDigits value="22"/>
						<xs:fractionDigits value="2"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="c117_Kp" minOccurs="0">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Calculated: Contributions to mandatory funded pension (code 1220 + code 1221 - code 1520)</xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:decimal">
						<xs:totalDigits value="22"/>
						<xs:fractionDigits value="2"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="c118_KohustKokku" minOccurs="0">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Calculated: Total taxes due (code 110 + code 114 + code 115 + code 116 + code 117) greater equal 0
          </xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:decimal">
						<xs:totalDigits value="22"/>
						<xs:fractionDigits value="2"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="c119_TagastKokku" minOccurs="0">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Calculated: Subject to refund (code 110 + code 114 + code 115 + code 116 + code 117) less than 0
          </xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:decimal">
						<xs:totalDigits value="22"/>
						<xs:fractionDigits value="2"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="c121_ParPohjusKood" minOccurs="0">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Code of the reason for creating an amended tax return if an amended tax return is applicable ( VMA – Errors in calculation of distributions and/or taxes and payments made to private individuals, VET – Distribution did not actually occur, VDV – Distribution attributed to incorrect person, VVK – Incorrect distribution code entered, TTM - Pension for incapacity for work declared on a retrospective basis, MTR – Liable to taxation in another country, DAM – Change in submitted data, DVK – Submitted data in the wrong month, VPV – Errors arising from a change in accounting software, AML – Change in previously submitted data or addition of data as a result of tax audit, MUU - Other)
          </xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:string">
						<xs:maxLength value="10"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="parPohjusTekst" minOccurs="0">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>If Other has been selected as the reason for amendment of the Form TSD, the description of the reason should be entered here
          </xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:string">
						<xs:maxLength value="1000"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="tsd_Inf1_0" type="tsdInf10" minOccurs="0"/>
			<xs:element name="tsd_L1_0" type="tsdL10" minOccurs="0"/>
			<xs:element name="tsd_L2_0" type="tsdL20" minOccurs="0"/>
			<xs:element name="tsd_L3_0" type="tsdL30" minOccurs="0"/>
			<xs:element name="tsd_L4_0" type="tsdL40" minOccurs="0"/>
			<xs:element name="tsd_L5_0" type="tsdL50" minOccurs="0"/>
			<xs:element name="tsd_L6_0" type="tsdL60" minOccurs="0"/>
			<xs:element name="tsd_L7_0" type="tsdL70" minOccurs="0"/>
			<xs:element name="tsd_L8_0" type="tsdL80" minOccurs="0"/>
			<xs:element name="tsd_Par_Pohj_LisaList" minOccurs="0">
				<xs:complexType>
					<xs:sequence>
						<xs:element name="tsd_Par_Pohj_Lisa" type="tsdParPohjLisa" maxOccurs="unbounded"/>
					</xs:sequence>
				</xs:complexType>
			</xs:element>
		</xs:all>
	</xs:complexType>
	<xs:complexType name="tsdInf10">
		<xs:all>
			<xs:element name="c13075_KpTmKokku" minOccurs="0">
				<xs:annotation>
					<xs:documentation>Total withheld income tax amount</xs:documentation>
				</xs:annotation>
				<xs:simpleType>
					<xs:restriction base="xs:decimal">
						<xs:totalDigits value="22"/>
						<xs:fractionDigits value="2"/>
					</xs:restriction>
				</xs:simpleType>
			</xs:element>
			<xs:element name="c13080_Osatahtsus" minOccurs="0">
